headline: Spotting Winners: UFP Industries (NASDAQ:UFPI) And Building Materials Stocks In Q4
summary: Quarterly earnings results are a good time to check in on a company’s progress, especially compared to its peers in the same sector. Today we are looking at UFP Industries (NASDAQ:UFPI) and the best and worst performers in the building materials industry.
